See the following wiki pages for the documentation:
http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:CollaborativeWatchlist/de
http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:CollaborativeWatchlist/en

You have to apply the mediawiki_core.patch in order to make
the CollaborativeWatchlist work with mediawiki. After applying the
patch append the following line to LocalSettings.php

require_once( "$IP/extensions/CollabWatchlist/CollabWatchlist.php" );

Then visit the Special:Collaborative_watchlist page.
